      "reason": "\u03b8 = heat kernel convolution with exp(-initial data/2\u03bd): EML-3. u = -2\u03bd\u00b7\u2202_x(log \u03b8): log of EML-3 = EML-3. Cole-Hopf \u2192 EML-3."
    },
